  "detailed_description": "<img src=\"https://steamcdn-a.akamaihd.net/steam/apps/291090/extras/IGTCED_steamTitle1.png?t=1469457473\" ><br>The green light flashes; another caller is on the line. You can tell right away it's going to be one of <i>those</i> calls... he's got a simple request, but you're caught between the bureaucracy that requires a gauntlet of security questions and a person who can barely remember his last address.<br><br><img src=\"https://steamcdn-a.akamaihd.net/steam/apps/291090/extras/IGTCED_steamTitle2.png?t=1469457473\" ><br>It would be so easy to let things slide. Just ease him through the questions, give him a hint or a nudge... or maybe you're done putting up with this. Your tolerance is shot and you're just not going to hold back on the snark. But either approach could end disastrously. You need this job. <br><br><img src=\"https://steamcdn-a.akamaihd.net/steam/apps/291090/extras/IGTCED_steamTitle3.png?t=1469457473\" ><br><strong><i>Features:</i></strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>A branching narrative pulled from personal experience.<br></li><li>Over 250 lines of fully-voiced dialogue.<br></li><li><strong>STEAM-EXCLUSIVE</strong> achievements and trading cards.</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<img src=\"https://steamcdn-a.akamaihd.net/steam/apps/291090/extras/IGTCED_steamTitle1.png?t=1469457473\" ><br>The green light flashes; another caller is on the line. You can tell right away it's going to be one of <i>those</i> calls... he's got a simple request, but you're caught between the bureaucracy that requires a gauntlet of security questions and a person who can barely remember his last address.<br><br><img src=\"https://steamcdn-a.akamaihd.net/steam/apps/291090/extras/IGTCED_steamTitle2.png?t=1469457473\" ><br>It would be so easy to let things slide. Just ease him through the questions, give him a hint or a nudge... or maybe you're done putting up with this. Your tolerance is shot and you're just not going to hold back on the snark. But either approach could end disastrously. You need this job. <br><br><img src=\"https://steamcdn-a.akamaihd.net/steam/apps/291090/extras/IGTCED_steamTitle3.png?t=1469457473\" ><br><strong><i>Features:</i></strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>A branching narrative pulled from personal experience.<br></li><li>Over 250 lines of fully-voiced dialogue.<br></li><li><strong>STEAM-EXCLUSIVE</strong> achievements and trading cards.</li></ul>",
  "short_description": "A lightly filtered experience pulled from the creator's (now former) day job in a customer service call centre, made interactive in a point-&amp;-click format. Lose politely, or lose spectacularly; the choice is yours.",
  "supported_languages": "English<strong>*</strong><br><strong>*</strong>languages with full audio support",
  "reviews": "\u201cIt\u2019s a game about seeing the other side, but raw and unsympathetic rather than didactic or apologetic. It\u2019s a game about how we\u2019ll feel the world\u2019s out to get us, no matter whether we\u2019re customer or operator. It\u2019s a game for everyone.\u201d<br><a href=\"http://www.rockpapershotgun.com/2013/05/03/wot-i-think-i-get-this-call-every-day/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\"  >Rock Paper Shotgun</a></a><br><br>\u201cAs mind-numbing and soul-draining as the game (and customer service in general) tend to be, any game whose ultimate lesson turns out to be, just maybe, be better to each other, is an experience worth having.\u201d<br>7/10 \u2013 <a href=\"https://steamcommunity.com/linkfilter/?url=http://www.gamespot.com/reviews/i-get-this-call-every-day-review/1900-6416467/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"  >Gamespot</a></a><br><br>\u201cI Get This Call Every Day captures the customer service life perfectly \u2013 the boredom, the bureaucracy, the bland environments \u2013 but possibly more than all that, it makes a strong statement for the need for human empathy in our everyday existence.\u201d<br>4/5 \u2013 <a href=\"https://steamcommunity.com/linkfilter/?url=http://www.scmp.com/culture/arts-entertainment/article/1992719/game-review-capturing-repetition-heart-office-work\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"  >South China Morning Post</a></a><br>",
  "header_image": "https://steamcdn-a.akamaihd.net/steam/apps/291090/header.jpg?t=1469457473",
